    <title>TOFEL_writing</title>
    <link href="http://jamessand.github.io/2022/07/20/TOFEL-writing/"/>
    <id>http://jamessand.github.io/2022/07/20/TOFEL-writing/</id>
    <published>2022-07-20T09:34:44.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-26T15:01:24.936Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="独立写作"><a href="#独立写作" class="headerlink" title="独立写作"></a>独立写作</h2><h3 id="开头段"><a href="#开头段" class="headerlink" title="开头段"></a>开头段</h3><p>三要素：</p><ol><li>社会背景</li><li>改写题中观点</li><li>自己观点</li></ol><h4 id="模板1"><a href="#模板1" class="headerlink" title="模板1"></a>模板1</h4><p>… has long been the center of public attention.</p><p>Some people claim that …</p><p>However, from my perspective, …</p><h4 id="模板2"><a href="#模板2" class="headerlink" title="模板2"></a>模板2</h4><p>将模板1的第一句话替换为</p><p>When it comes to …, opinions vary, based on people’s diverse backgrounds, experiences, and values. </p><h6 id="模板中的替换"><a href="#模板中的替换" class="headerlink" title="模板中的替换"></a>模板中的替换</h6><blockquote><p><u>Some</u> people claim that</p></blockquote><p>&#x3D; a large propotion of</p><p>&#x3D; the vast majority of </p><blockquote><p>Some people <u>claim</u> that</p></blockquote><p>&#x3D; argue &#x2F; <strong>deem</strong> &#x2F; <strong>reckon</strong> </p><p>&#x3D; <strong>opt to do</strong> </p><blockquote><p><u>However</u>, from my perspective</p></blockquote><p>&#x3D; Nevertheless</p><p>&#x3D; Nonetheless</p><blockquote><p>However, from my perspective</p></blockquote><p>&#x3D; as far as I see</p><p>&#x3D; as far as I am concerned</p><p>&#x3D; from my point of view</p><p>&#x3D; in my opinion </p><h6 id="表达观点"><a href="#表达观点" class="headerlink" title="表达观点"></a>表达观点</h6><p>xxx brings more merits &#x2F; benefits</p><p>this view does not hold water</p><h3 id="结尾段"><a href="#结尾段" class="headerlink" title="结尾段"></a>结尾段</h3><p><strong>模板</strong></p><p>(1) All in all &#x2F; To sum up &#x2F; In conclusion &#x2F; In a nutshell &#x2F; On the whole, …</p><p>(2) </p><ul><li><p>from what has been discussed above, </p></li><li><p>taking into account all the factors discussed above, </p></li><li><p>considering all the factors above, </p></li><li><p>from all the analysis above,</p></li></ul><p>(3) it is <u>safe &#x2F; natural &#x2F; reasonable</u> to <u>come to &#x2F; draw &#x2F; reach &#x2F; arrive at</u> the conclusion that + 全文总论点同义改写</p><h3 id="段落展开"><a href="#段落展开" class="headerlink" title="段落展开"></a>段落展开</h3><h4 id="举例方法"><a href="#举例方法" class="headerlink" title="举例方法"></a>举例方法</h4><p>举例技巧1  具体化 + 有效细节展开</p><p>举例技巧2 情节跌宕起伏，前后对比</p><blockquote><p>一个健康的例子，可以背一下</p></blockquote><p>Take my friend Jake, for an example. He used to love deep-fried food and sugar, staying at home all day <strong>without any physical activity</strong>(这里activity是活动，不可数). But when he was diagnosed with <strong>diabetes</strong> last year, he decided to make a change. </p><p>Now, apart from <strong>hitting the gym</strong> regularly and spending at least two hours there, he plays tennis every day with his wife. His weight went from 255 pounds to 180 pounds, and he has <strong>gotten rid of the disease</strong>. </p><h6 id="个例-x2F-事例"><a href="#个例-x2F-事例" class="headerlink" title="个例 &#x2F; 事例"></a>个例 &#x2F; 事例</h6><p>For example, …</p><p>Take … as an example.</p><p>My brother is a good <strong>case in point</strong>.</p><p>This point is best illustrated by the case of …</p><blockquote><p>一个电子产品的例子，可以背一下</p></blockquote><p>My little sister Amy is a good case in point. She used to be a <strong>painfully shy</strong> girl with few friends, since she spent most of her time studying and had no shared moments with friends. </p><p>However, things began to change after I taught her how to play Honor of Kings, <strong>a multiplayer online battle arena video game</strong>. This game allows her to <strong>connect with</strong> people and get feedback on how well she is playing. Besides, it creates plenty of topics to share with people around her, and now every day she plays the game with her classmates and they become <strong>faithful friends</strong>. </p><h6 id="举例常用细节"><a href="#举例常用细节" class="headerlink" title="举例常用细节"></a>举例常用细节</h6><ol><li>高中生 -&gt; 学校</li><li>工作者-&gt; 公司 + 工作职责</li><li>大学生 -&gt; 学校 + 专业</li></ol><p>高中: </p><p>​the school affiliated to Renmin University of China</p><p>工作者：</p><p>​Take my uncle Smith as an example. He is in charge of bussiness while working at Microsoft.  </p><p>​be in charge of (负责)</p>]]></content>
    
    
